overview: The user wanted to elevate the visual appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, which previously had a generic, template-like appearance.
  The assistant undertook a comprehensive aesthetic overhaul, starting with a
  detailed analysis of the existing design. Key decisions included adopting a
  calming, sleep-themed color palette, redesigning the main form layout with
  subtle decorative elements and an improved progress indicator, and enhancing
  the welcome and report sections with more engaging visuals. All form
  components, such as checkboxes, radio buttons, and sliders, were polished for
  better visual feedback. The styling was consistently applied across all
  questionnaire sections, replacing old gray boxes with refined card-style
  groupings. The outcome is an app with a professional, trustworthy, and
  visually appealing interface that aligns with a sleep health assessment
  experience.
